set webhook URL on LINE Developers
 URL can be specified on AWS Lambda - functions - Designer
  -> add AWS Gateway as a trigger
press verify button on LINE Developers with URL above being set(something like https://{domain}.execute-api.{arn}.amazonaws.com/default/{function-name})
 -if error is displayed, there might be an error in function code.

